{"tid":1823964,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"不得不講句，有啲男仔就係嬌情","createTime":"2020-01-14T05:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T07:55:57.000Z","uid":129222,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5d7f9dffa94c838adc7625d3136ec3c9247cb9","tid":1823964,"uid":129222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:52:54.000Z","msg":"最近同啲男性朋友出黎食飯<br />\n少不別大家會講吓溝女果啲嘢<br />\n其中一個朋友都暗戀咗一個大學識嘅女仔幾年，成日like 人地ig 啲post，大學果時又成日幫人拎source, 到畢咗業又間唔中約人食飯（不過係我個朋友埋單）<br />\n佢見女神ig 無男仔相以為人地單身緊，咁早排聖誕就鼓起勇氣同人表白，唔洗問，緊係衰咗啦<br />\n果吓我想同佢講人地當你傻仔黎，唔好咁賤自己貼埋去啦<br />\n不過其他朋友果時同佢講 &ldquo;你好仔黎嘅，比得時間肯定追到佢&rdquo;<br />\n到早幾日係條街到我見到佢女神同另外一個男仔拖手行街，先記起有件咁嘅事<br />\n問題黎啦，到底應唔應該同我朋友講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5caaca18fc68cb58f9ce419d3db7c8c8423079c","tid":1823964,"uid":28845,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:55:48.000Z","msg":"俾佢早啲醒"},{"pid":"d1f3e9c7e49acb7d3ba93eb39c6227dadf0a9eb8","tid":1823964,"uid":48579,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"關矯情咩事"},{"pid":"f5d7b9cb6aaa083e0e382efe17a2cca3a4d22a7a","tid":1823964,"uid":129222,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1f3e9c7e49acb7d3ba93eb39c6227dadf0a9eb8","tid":1823964,"uid":48579,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"關矯情咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:01:01.000Z","msg":"佢自己拎黎賤囉<br />\n人地明顯對佢無feel仲係到發白日夢<br />\n諗住會回心轉意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d0d603e37cb37bc634ea827945d3b2d39fe95d","tid":1823964,"uid":48579,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"f5d7b9cb6aaa083e0e382efe17a2cca3a4d22a7a","tid":1823964,"uid":129222,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1f3e9c7e49acb7d3ba93eb39c6227dadf0a9eb8","tid":1823964,"uid":48579,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"re